description: Makes configuring tracing easy and standardized for .NET Core, .NET Standard, and .NET Framework.

If you want to render some video sequence, and do not want to touch DirectShow or depend on command-line utilities - SharpAvi may be what you need.

Writing uncompressed AVI does not require any external dependencies, it's pure .NET code. Files are produced in compliance with the OpenDML extensions which allow (nearly) unlimited file size (no 2GB limit).

Video is created by supplying individual in-memory bitmaps (byte arrays) and audio samples. Included are implementations of encoders for Motion JPEG (requires WPF), MPEG-4 (requires external VfW codecs) and MP3 (requires LAME binaries). Asynchronous writing/encoding is supported.
summary: A simple library for creating video files in AVI format.

Active Query Builder ASP.NET Edition is a Visual SQL Query Builder for ASP.NET WebForms, MVC and Core 2.0 environments with full support of all popular database servers and appropriate SQL dialects. Working with Active Query Builder the end-user can combine visual query building with direct SQL query text editing, preview sub-query results. Active Query Builder allows for parsing of complex SQL queries for their visual representation as well as for programmatic analysis and modification.
This package should be used in MVC .NET projects. Packages for WebForms and ASP.NET Core environments are available separately.
summary: Visual SQL Query Builder for your ASP.NET MVC project.
